This extension captures the elegance and strength of one of the game's most powerful characters, bringing her presence to your browser with every new tab.

Features:
🎨 High-quality live wallpaper of Durandal from Honkai Impact 3.
🌐 Customizable search bar to use your preferred search engine.
🕒 Clock and date display for a more functional and stylish layout.
🔗 Quick-access shortcuts for easy navigation to your favorite websites.
Feel the power and grace of Durandal as she takes over your new tab, enhancing your browsing experience with the energy of Honkai Impact 3. Perfect for fans of the game looking to add a touch of action and beauty to their browser.
